## Git

Several issues were encountered.

Problems:

- Accidentally initialized multiple repositories.
- Worked in the wrong Relay directory.
- GitHub Pages initially deployed placeholder content.
- HTML and CSS became mismatched after multiple AI edits.
- Rebase conflicts while syncing with origin.
- Landing page required complete rebuild.

Resolved by:

- Rebasing onto origin/main
- Resolving merge conflicts
- Replacing landing page with synchronized HTML/CSS
- Successfully pushing final commit

Final commit:

e6a4537

Repository is clean and synchronized.

---

# Lessons Learned

Never let HTML and CSS evolve independently.

Always regenerate both files together when making major visual changes.

Verify Git directory before beginning work.

Avoid creating duplicate repositories inside Documents.

